{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_168","type":"agent_message","text":"Implemented autosave for partial composition drafts and committed it as `441fe16` (`feat(prompt-68): autosave drafts and partials`).\n\nThe backend now writes a rolling session-level draft snapshot to object storage, upserts a single `draft_text_snapshot` asset record instead of creating unbounded rows, refreshes that snapshot on autosave/segment-complete/manual manuscript changes, and hydrates composition resume text from the snapshot when job metadata is incomplete. The main changes are in [composition_jobs.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/services/composition_jobs.py), [session_hydration.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/services/session_hydration.py), [assets.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/services/assets.py), [assets.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/repositories/assets.py), [sessions.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/repositories/sessions.py), and [paths.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/storage/paths.py). I also added coverage in [test_asset_service.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/tests/test_asset_service.py), [test_session_hydration_service.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/tests/test_session_hydration_service.py), and [test_story_tools.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/tests/test_story_tools.py), plus updated [storage-buckets-and-prefixes.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/docs/storage-buckets-and-prefixes.md).\n\nVerification:\n- `pytest backend/tests/test_asset_service.py backend/tests/test_session_hydration_service.py backend/tests/test_story_tools.py -q` -> `43 passed`\n- `pytest backend/tests/test_asset_service.py backend/tests/test_session_hydration_service.py backend/tests/test_story_tools.py backend/tests/test_session_api.py backend/tests/test_session_service.py -q` -> `108 passed`\n- `cd backend && python -m ruff check app tests` -> passed\n- `python -m compileall backend/app` -> passed\n- Browser refresh QA against the compose stack passed and produced [prompt-68-refresh-resume.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-68-refresh-resume.png)\n\nThe required reviewer summary is written at [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/68_autosave_drafts_and_partial_outputs/summary.md)."}}
